{
  "stem": "13141.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he said on the telephone, he said, take the IRT train, you know, and get off at 72nd Street, and look for rooming house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, they say 'room to let.'",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- it was not easy to get on the subway with two suitcases.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they had these turn-- what do you call it, where you get in and out, you know, where you drop your nickle?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the time, you dropped a nickle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the fare.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got off at 72nd street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found there were plenty of rooms to let.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got one that cost me $3.50 a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Walk up four flights, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was under the roof, you know, where the roof goes this way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very hot in summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had to open that little roof window, you know, with that-- with a-- with that hook so it stayed open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, well, there's also a little story, if I may.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My English wasn't too good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were two girls who were living on the same floor, so they were rooming with each other, staying in the same room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, what time do you have to leave?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told them my time so we could coordinate our time to go to the bathroom, because the rooms didn't have a bathroom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a bathroom on the floor, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was the first one to go to the bathroom in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said they would have to come in at certain time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the bathroom had only a little hook, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I put that hook on from the inside-- I thought I had put it on, but apparently I hadn't.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was shaving, and the door opened, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
